N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5505.3 - Parades, assemblages or demonstrations

State Regulations

No parades, assemblages or demonstrations of any kind shall
be held in or upon the facilities without the express prior written permission
of the authority. Notes
